flowchart LR
  S[Session s=<i1,...,iT>] --> E[Session Encoder E]
  E --> U[u_*]
  U --> CI[Context Indexing: Top-C similar sessions]
  CI --> C[Context set C_*={(u_c,v_c)}]
  C --> D[Deterministic Summary c_*=Agg(phi(u_c,v_c))]
  D --> P[Prior p(eta|C_*)]
  D --> Q[Posterior q(eta|C_*,u_*,v_*) train only]
  P --> Z[Latent samples eta^(k)]
  Q -.KL.-> L[ELBO Loss]
  Z --> DEC[Multi-sample Decoder psi]
  U --> DEC
  D --> DEC
  DEC --> R[q_* = average decoded queries]
  R --> H[Full-item Ranking q_*^T e(i)]
  H --> TOP[Top-N / HR / MRR / COV]
  H -.CE.-> L
